{"tid":2010380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(報復?)支那擬向澳洲徵收大麥進口關稅","createTime":"2020-05-10T11:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T14:04:23.000Z","uid":75656,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ab91b26441d709346f39bfb5f3ce64faedfabb01","tid":2010380,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"Several major Australian grain groups have issued a joint statement today saying the industry understands China is &quot;potentially proposing to place tariffs on barley imported from Australia as a result of their ongoing anti-dumping and countervailing duties investigation&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The yet-to-be-finalised tariffs may include a dumping margin of up to 73.6 per cent and a subsidy margin of up to 6.9 per cent for barley imported from Australia,&quot; it said.<br />\n<br />\nThe subsidy claims are understood to refer to Australia's fuel rebate and drought support measures, and together with the dumping tariff would effectively put an end to Australia's barley trade with China.<br />\n<br />\nGovernment sources suggest the investigation could be used as a cover to impose the tariffs, in retaliation against Australia's push for the COVID-19 inquiry. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-05-10/coronavirus-china-australia-trade-tension-barley-tariff/12232426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2020-05-10%2Fcoronavirus-china-australia-trade-tension-barley-tariff%2F12232426&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQoTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=bfe3c9cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-05-10/coronavirus-china-australia-trade-tension-barley-tariff/12232426</a>"},{"pid":"4a9bdbbb757b66d44cbf5107ed8777a6875d0eac","tid":2010380,"uid":258578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da01787ba46eb9aacad6893fe07a62d76bf0e7bc","tid":2010380,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislik